## ğŸ§ª CLI Configuration (Sample Commands)

### ğŸ”¹ VLAN Configuration (Switch)
```bash
vlan 10
 name SALES
vlan 20
 name HR


ğŸ”¹ Trunk Port Configuration

interface fa0/1
 switchport mode trunk

ğŸ”¹ Inter-VLAN Routing (Delhi Router)

interface g0/0.10
 encapsulation dot1Q 10
 ip address 192.168.0.1 255.255.255.0

interface g0/0.20
 encapsulation dot1Q 20
 ip address 172.16.0.1 255.255.255.0

ğŸ”¹ DHCP Configuration (Delhi Router)

ip dhcp pool VLAN10
 network 192.168.0.0 255.255.255.0
 default-router 192.168.0.1
 dns-server 8.8.8.8

ip dhcp pool VLAN20
 network 172.16.0.0 255.255.255.0
 default-router 172.16.0.1
 dns-server 8.8.8.8

ğŸ”¹ WAN Serial Configuration

interface s0/0/0
 ip address 10.0.0.1 255.255.255.252
 clock rate 64000
 no shutdown

ğŸ”¹ OSPF Configuration (Both Enterprise Routers)

router ospf 1
 network 192.168.0.0 0.0.0.255 area 0
 network 172.16.0.0 0.0.0.255 area 0
 network 10.0.0.0 0.0.0.3 area 0
 network 150.0.0.0 0.0.0.255 area 0

ğŸ”¹ Mumbai Router DHCP (For Home Router)

ip dhcp pool HOME_ROUTER
 network 150.0.0.0 255.255.255.0
 default-router 150.0.0.1

